data.description: Welcome to your new home in exclusive Marsh Creek, where resort-style amenities and luxurious living come together seamlessly. From the moment you walk through the front door, you'll be captivated by the grandeur of high ceilings, an open floor plan, and exquisite architectural details that define this residence.  As you enter, you'll be greeted by an inviting foyer that sets the tone for the rest of the home. The open-concept layout connects the spacious living area, ideal for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy evenings by the fireplace. Large windows flood the space with natural light, accentuating the beauty of the interior.  The chef's kitchen is a culinary delight, featuring new appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage space. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or preparing a family meal, this kitchen is sure to inspire your inner chef.  Retreat to the master suite, a private oasis boasting a luxurious ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms are generously sized and offer versatility for guest rooms, home offices, or creative spaces.  Step outside to your own outdoor haven and enjoy spectacular sunsets over the marsh or a swim in the pool. The large fenced yard provides a serene setting for relaxation and outdoor activities. The patio is perfect for al fresco dining, while the lush greenery creates a peaceful retreat.  Living in this golf community means access to world-class amenities. Whether it's a round of golf on the pristine course, a leisurely day by the pool, or socializing at the community clubhouse, you'll find endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation.  Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining, this home offers both convenience and comfort. You'll be just minutes to the beach and Historic Downtown St. Augustine. With modern amenities and classic charm, this property presents a unique opportunity to experience a sophisticated lifestyle in a sought-after neighborhood.
